vote.title: Authorize Supplemental Agreement No. 3 to the contract 20-1682 with US Intelliwake LLC, for the software licensing fee to provide electronic invoicing and reporting resources to local governments through the North Texas Share Cooperative Purchasing Program - Not to exceed $179,737.03, increasing the contract amount from $318,413.98 to $498,151.01 -  Financing:  Bond Program Administration Fund
